name: Insector LD48
description:
Insector - A game where you are an ant from a rival colony, who travels deep-inside the enemies anthill to kill their queen! Space to jump and again in air to double jump, Left Mouse to attack, 'V' key or Middle mouse to change ant and Right mouse to use special ability.

Created by Jaxson Gould, Jesse Zavala & Scott Bowsher
